Automaton: examplebtslave
	Class: slave
	 States: 
	 State btinit		do wait for bt
	 State watch		do nothing
	 State sonarflag	do beep, send sonar
	 State colorflag	do beep, send newcolorfound
	 State measurement	do consume package, beep, beep, lower temparm, measure temperature, send action done
	 State finished		do beep, beep, beep, send alldone
	 
	 Arrows:
	 btinit -> watch		if (and true)
	 watch -> sonarflag		if (and sonar senses something)
	 watch -> colorflag		if (and colorsensor reads red color is new) (and colorsensor reads blue color is new) (and colorsensor reads green color is new)
	 sonarflag -> watch		if (and true)
	 colorflag -> watch		if (and timeout 30 sec) //voor robuustheid?
	 colorflag -> measurement 	if (and receive action done)
	 measurement -> finished	if (and all colours found)
	 measurement -> watch		if (and true)
	
	 Start state: btinit
	 End state: finished
